  <text>
     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="94"/>
   <lg>
      <l>With heart I craue, reade, viewe and see,</l>
      <l>If better you haue, impart it with me.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>Nowe slaunderer say thy worst,</l>
      <l>with malice and defame:</l>
      <l>In God I onely trust,</l>
      <l>all glory to his name.</l>
   </lg>
   <p>
      <pb facs="94"/>
